'''Ousmane William Mbaye''' (yavutse 1952), yavukiye muri  [[Senegali|Senegal]] azwi mu gukora filimi .  Mbaye azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa documentaire ''Mère-Bi'' ''ishimwa cyane'' na film Doomi Ngacc, ''Fresque'' na ''Kemtiyu, Cheikh Anta'' .  Usibye gukora amafilime, ni numu producer mukuru, utunganya umurongo, umwanditsi wa sinema, producer wamahanga, umuyobozi wamafoto, uwandika amajwi, umuyobozi ushinzwe umusaruro, umwanditsi, na producer. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1952 i [[Paris]], mu [[Bufaransa]]. Nyina, Annette Mbaye d'Erneville akomoka muri senengali .  

== Umwuga ==
Mbaye yahuguye muri Conservatoire Libre du Cinéma Français (Konserwatori Yubusa ya Sinema y'Abafaransa). Nyuma yize muri kaminuza ya Paris 8 Vincennes-Saint-Denis aho yatangiriye gukina amashusho. Amaze kubona impamyabumenyi, yimukiye muri [[Senegali]] . Nyuma yaje kuba umuyobozi wungirije. Kuva 1990 kugeza 1997, yabaye umuhuzabikorwa nuwashinze Rencontres Cinématographiques ya Dakar (RECIDAK). 

Mu 1979, yakoze kandi ayobora filime ye ya mbere ya ''Doomi Ngacc'' . Mugufi yatsindiye Bronze Tanit mu iserukiramuco rya Filime ya Carthage . Kuva mu 2000, yatangiye gukora documentaire nka ''Président Dia'' na ''Kemtiyu, Cheikh Anta'' .  Mu 2003, yakoze documentaire ngufi ''Xalima la plume'' yerekeye umucuranzi wa Senegal Seydina Insa Wade. Nyuma yaho gato yatsindiye igihembo cya Documentaire muri Festival ya Milan . Mu 2005, yayoboye documentaire ''Fer et verre'', yibanze ku muhanzi wa plastiki wo muri Senegal Anta Germane Gaye . Muri 2008, yakoze ''Mère-Bi'' ngufi, ishingiye kuri nyina.  

Mu mwaka wa 2016, yakoze documentaire yerekana ubuzima bwa ''Kemtiyu, Cheikh Anta'' ivuga ku buzima bw’amateka ya Senegal, umuganga, n’umunyapolitiki Cheikh Anta Diop .  Iyi filime yakiriwe neza n'abayinenga kandi yerekanwa mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.   Yahawe igihembo cya EU / ACP mu iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou (FESPACO) 2017. 

